{"tid":1284162,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"反對DQ: 炸爆選管會電郵","createTime":"2019-07-04T05:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T15:32:03.000Z","uid":270374,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ccc83604be544ece4d23c7d902fbd4380159d76c","tid":1284162,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T05:01:29.000Z","msg":"區議會換屆選舉將於11月24日舉行，選管會早前發表區議會選舉活動建議指引，建議在區選中引入「確認書」制度，要求參選人簽署聲明擁護《基本法》及保證效忠香港特別行政區，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">諮詢期本月10日屆滿。民主派議員批評政府利用確認書DQ參選人，剝削選舉權利，呼籲市民以提意見促選管會撤銷「確認書」。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n可以從三個方式表達：郵寄（香港灣仔港灣道二十五號海港中心十樓選管會秘書處）、傳真（2511 1682）及電郵（eacenq@eac.hk）。<br />\n<br />\n原文﹕<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190703/59785123\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190703%2F59785123&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFIxR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=338ad712\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190703%2F59785123&h=db1cbf22\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190703/59785123</a><br />\n意見書Template: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/2332346906857804/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F200976479994868%2Fposts%2F2332346906857804%2F&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFIxR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=09471394\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/2332346906857804/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">休息但不能鬆懈，兄弟加油!!!! </span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6cdbd3d7e40104627ba9cad70ed63690ece0abb4","tid":1284162,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:29:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e9d0d6a16acda9f2fc22e38ab7edfcfacd0291","tid":1284162,"